Install RVM with gemset rvm 1.9.2@orso
Install Postgres

Start Postgres with command (for homebrew) /usr/local/Cellar/postgresql/9.0.4/bin/pg_ctl start -l logfile -D /usr/local/var/postgres/


To create postgres user and database:

$ psql template1
psql (9.0.4)
Type "help" for help.

template1=# CREATE USER ideas WITH PASSWORD '123';
CREATE ROLE
template1=# CREATE DATABASE ideas_test;
CREATE DATABASE
template1=# GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE ideas_test to ideas;
GRANT
template1=# CREATE DATABASE ideas_development;
CREATE DATABASE
template1=# GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE ideas_development to ideas;
GRANT
template1=# \q
